title: Places I've Been
name: Places I've Been
description:
A Map by Wskolits

This is a map of the places I have been in the world.

properties.name: Ft. Lauderdale, Florida
properties.description: Posted by Wskolits4780 N. State Road 7 Building E, Suite 100, Fort Lauderdale, FL, 33319I used to visit my grandparents here in the fall and winter since they would live six months in florida and six months in Long Island, NY. They lived in a community of large mobile homes (that aren\'t mobile) full of the elderly.

properties.name: Asheville, North Carolina
properties.description: Posted by Wskolits22 Woodfin St, Asheville, NCThis is not too far away, but I go here to visit my cousin, katie, and her dad. She goes to college there.

properties.name: Carson City, Nevada
properties.description: Posted by Wskolits2749 N. Carson St., Carson City, NV 89706My dad and I came here driving around California. There are some historic districts here that we checked out - some western style streets, etc. We also went to mono lake not too far away.

properties.name: Hamilton, Bermuda
properties.description: Posted by WskolitsBermudaI went on a cruise this past summer to Bermuda, and we stopped for a few days in Hamilton. I went night-time snorkeling here and I got stung by jellyfish - it was definitely not fun getting stung.

properties.name: Hilton San Francisco Financial District Hotel
properties.description: Posted by Wskolits 750 Kearny St, San Francisco, CAAt yet another conference, my dad took me out to San Francisco for his educational group Gear Up that he works with. We spent a few extra days there as well to see the area. We also traveled over to hike Yosemite.

properties.name: La Quinta Inn Portland Convention Center
properties.description: Posted by Wskolits 431 Ne Multnomah St, Portland, ORMy Dad took me a few summers ago to a conference he had to go to in Portland. We stayed a few extra days to go hiking and check out Mt. Hood. We hiked around it and up it some. It was very beautiful.

properties.name: Orlando, FL
properties.description: Posted by WskolitsOrlando, FLI have been to Orlando a few times. I have been here mainly to go with family and friends to Disney and Universal Studios.

properties.name: Panama City Beach
properties.description: Posted by Wskolits  panama city beachI had some wonderful seafood while on vacation here at a crab shack. I definitely recommend this place to anyone who just wants a short vacation to chill at the beach.

properties.name: Waldorf-Astoria Hotel
properties.description: Posted by Wskolits This is a beautiful and famous hotel in New York City. It is usually quite pricy, but my family somehow received a special deal to get to stay here for a few nights in the city to see some broadshow shows, etc.

properties.name: Yosemite Bug Hostel
properties.description: Posted by WskolitsCaliforniaThis is a hostel that I stayed at in Yosemite. I went on some of the tours and hikes that were offered by this hostel. I went on one sunset hike that was extremely beautiful.
